CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 2, 2009

[Cite as 11/02/09 Case Announcements #2, 2009-Ohio-5775.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2009-1547. Ohio Consumers’ Counsel v. Pub. Util. Comm.

The Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 07-1080-GA-AIR and 07-1081-GA-ALT. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the corrected joint motion for procedural stay,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
